{"title":"警告美帝","authors":["陶钝"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":9,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"警告美帝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陶钝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝国主义睁开眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别拿中国当从前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱弄大炮就弄炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱开轮船就开轮船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从共产党来领导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨人竖起了大铁拳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁敢上来碰一碰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管保打你个鼻青、眼肿、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头破血流、腰断、腿折，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身上下都伤残！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说这话你不信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看一看中国建设这九年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这九年，不简单，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九年胜过五千年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农业生产大跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社运动正当前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁、粮食和棉花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻了一番又一番。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国青壮年都是兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编班、编队、编营又编团。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军把守在国防前线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准备着把敌人坚决、彻底、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干净、全部消灭完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些力量还不算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有那同盟兄弟强大的苏联。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝国主义不健忘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想一想朝鲜败仗才五年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“三八线”刚刚越了一步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十四万美军全玩完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台湾海峡好比上甘岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坟墓都给你准备全。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你若胆敢再挑衅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死神就在你面前！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}